t care for every patient in hospital, optional services go beyond the necessary care. These include optional services of medical and medical care (chief physician contract) or accommodation in a comfort ward or in a comfort room. Optional services can be used by privately insured persons, self-payers as well as persons with statutory health insurance. Please clarify with your health insurance company in good time before concluding a contract to what extent you are insured for the additional services. Legally binding information on clinic costs and tariff issues is provided exclusively by the administration of the University Hospital. Contractual general conditions Please inform yourself about the general terms and conditions of the University Hospital T√ºbingen. Contractual general conditions Enquiries If you have any queries about treatment costs or your statement, please contact the patient administration. Patient management Model contract for elective service by chief physician Model contract for optional room Information about the comfort room Certificates and Associations Focus: Top Nationales Krankenhaus 2024 Die deutschen Universit√§tsklinika Kooperation f√ºr Transparenz und Qualit√§t im Gesundheitswesen Qualit√§tspartnerschaft mit der PKV Blauer Sterne Betrieb Erfolgsfaktor Familie Die Altersvorsorge f√ºr den √ñffentlichen Dienst Back to top Emergency 112 rescue service germany 116 117 on-duty medical service germany 0761 19240 poisoning germany Childbirth Emergencies and wards Emergency stand-by The University Hospital Our Institutions A-Z Facts and figures History Quality Management and administration Communications and Media Relations Donations Patients and Visitors International patients Outpatient appointments Hospitalization Feedback Faculty of Medicine Doctoral Studies Research Institutes Deanery and faculty council ¬© 2024 University Hospital and Faculty of Medicine T√ºbingen Career Contact Imprint Privacy Policy Accessibility Cookie Einstellungen Bi